                            <comment id="12953881" author="gertvanthienen" created="Tue, 24 Nov 2009 13:02:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch solves the issue by always returning the aggregated result.  Can someone take a quick look before I apply it?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There&apos;s only one problem with this fix &amp;#8211; up to now, if a user mistakenly configured an @RecipientList-annotated method with the recipientList(bean(...)) call, the end result would still be ok because the bean(...) call would result in the list of endpoints being sent back.       This fix would break that behavior.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
